A (very) basic contact form example using Play-Mailer

https://github.com/playframework/play-mailer

https://www.playframework.com/documentation/2.6.x/ModuleDirectory#Emailer-Plugin-(Java-and-Scala)

Before using:

1. Configure the mail server settings in application.conf - at end of file.
   (The play mailer module configuration can be found in app/playconfig)
2. Modify the mail message in the contactSubmit() method (see HomeController.java)
3. Read the Play-Mailer docs for more configuration options (attachments, HTML email, etc.)

